{
  "stem": "26142.18",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "To make the story short, I had six blood transfusions, two one in a row, and three in every second, third day.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, and, and so, and all of a sudden, I started, started to feel alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I think this was this Major [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Killinger ?] that I looked for when I spoke to this, to this Colonel Walter J.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Fellenz that liberated the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, and he said that, that I should contact the Pentagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My son dead.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We couldn't, couldn't locate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Maybe it's not the-- maybe I have the name wrong.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And, and so we were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And, and four, five weeks later, on June the nine, I was sent into a regular hospital that was one of the finest hospitals the Germans had built for the Air Force, the German Air Force.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was called the Luftwaffen Hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And over there, I had, for more than one year's time, more than one year's time, I had over a 102 fever every day.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I had pleurisy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were pumping gallons of, gallons of water from my, my lungs out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But I was 25 years old then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I was-- in spite of all the, all the, the, the illness and the, and the, and the fever-- I was able in the morning breakfast, to have a good breakfast.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I kept on gaining.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Almost each week, I gained a kilogram, two kilogram, which was two to three to four pounds a week.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And a year later, I regained my weight to 80, to 80 kilograms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "At that time, that was my normal weight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And, in 19-- so I stayed in this, in this hospital till 1947.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
